16. Qa3 Qxa3 17. Nxa3 Bb7 18. Bc5 Rfd8 19. Rxd8+ Rxd8 20. Nc4 Nd7 21. Be3 c5
22. f3 $14 {[%csl Gc4,Rc5][%cal Gf1e2,Ge3c5] The first player has a slight
