Qc7 15. Rfe1 Bd7 16. g3 (16. a3 $5) 16... Rfe8 (16... Rae8 17. a3 Ng4 18. b4 h6
19. Bc1 N4e5 20. Nxe5 Nxe5 21. Be2 b5 22. Bf4 Rc8 {With a complex game where
