give up the pawn on h7 after} 18... Rad8 19. h5 Ne7 20. Bxh7+ Kg7 21. h6+ Kh8
$44 {The pair of bishops, the semi-open g-file and the mass of central pawns
offer full compensation for the sacrificed pawn.}) 19. Qd2 $14 {0-1 (38)
