O-O-O Ne7 (12... b5 13. Nxc6 Qxc6 14. Bd4 {[%csl Gd3,Gd4]} Bb7 15. Kb1 Rad8 16.
Bxf6 gxf6 17. Qe3 {[%cal Ge3h6]} Kg7 18. Nd4 Qc7 19. Qh3 {[%csl Rh7][%cal
Gh3h7]} Rh8 20. Bxb5 $14 {White wins a pawn, with a preferable position due to
the exposed black king.}) 13. Bg5 Ned5 14. Kb1 b5 15. Ne5 Qc7 16. Rhe1 Bb7 17.
Bc1 $14 {[%cal Gf2f4,Gg2g4] Reaching a fighting position, where the first
player has a small plus in his favour.}) 12. O-O-O Qc7 (12... O-O {Transposing
