{White has an extra pawn in this asymmetrical structure. His general plan is
to finish development and start advancing his queenside pawns. Some thematic
moves are Bb5-Be3(d2 or b2 too)-Nbd2 and moving the king to the queenside if
possible via c2-b3.}  *

