a5 $1 {This knight sacrifice is analysed on different occasions in Chapter XX.}
19. h5 g5 20. Be4 Ra7 21. Rhe1 Rb8 $13) 17. c4 $1 {[%csl Rd7][%cal Gd1d7]} Bxf2
$2 (17... O-O $1 {was the best chance.} 18. h5 g5 19. cxd5 cxd5 20. Kb1 Bd6 21.
