{This is the classic structure of three white pawns against two black on the
queenside. It can be reached via many opening after both 1.e4 and 1.d4. Next,
we will see two examples of how to generate weaknesses on the kingside and
unbalance the game. In the third example, we will examine a typical endgame.} 
*

